title.narrative: Procurement of Services for Economic Empowerment of the Poorest Programme

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of Services for Economic Empowerment of the Poorest Programme) is a component of Economic Empowerment of the Poorest reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £12,865,103. This component benefits Bangladesh, and works in the following sector(s): Social Protection, Environmental policy and administrative management, Urban development and management, Rural development. , with the following implementing partners: Harewelle International Limited. The start date is 01-11-2005 and the end date is 30-09-2016.
